Package: bcg.annotation
Title: Manually label heartbeats in a ballistocardiogram
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Max",
           family = "Czapanskiy",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "maxczap@stanford.edu",
           comment = c("ORCID-ID" = "0000-0002-6302-905X"))
Description: bcg.annotation provides a Shiny app for manually labeling
    heartbeats in ballistocardiom data. Designed for diving animals, it
    presents the dive profile alongside a jerk profile. Low magnitude
    peaks in jerk during periods without motion indicate heart beats.
